SUMMARY:Youngberg Hill Vineyard & Inn - Memorial Weekend
DESCRIPTION:Memorial Weekend\nYoungberg Hill will be open from 11:00 to 
 5:00 on Saturday\, Sunday\, & Monday. We will be highlighting our 2007 J
 ordan & Natasha Block Pinot Noir as well as our newly released 2009 Pino
 t Gris. We will have cheeses\, breads\, and treats available\, plus the 
 greatest view.\n\nTasting fee of $5\, complimentary tastings for our Win
 e Club members. \n
